Summary: Set of cloud computing automation utilities
Home-page: http://sourceforge.net/projects/balloon-foam
Author: Alexey Petrov
Author-email: alexey.petrov.nnov@gmail.com
License: Apache License, Version 2.0
Description: These utilities provide seemless mode for:
                - accessing to cloud;
                - deploying user specified data and functionality to be run on this data;
                - launching of the cloud specified task;
                - storing of output data into cloud;
                - fectching of these output results from cloud;
                - other miscellaneous functions
